beer.beer_description:
Brewed with a blend of pale and crystal malts, and both kettle and dry hopped with Ella, our Garden Ale has a citrus fruit aroma, balanced with a clean malt character and an easy bitter finish.

It’s the perfect sessionable brew, best enjoyed in your favourite beer garden or in your own backyard. 3.8% alc/vol
